Step to create package.json
<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
***NodeJs must be install in the system 

1> Open the cmd
2> go inside the folder
3> npm init    
4> Answer all questions
5> type yes

>>>>>>>>>>>>>Step to install npm package<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
*NodeJs must be install in the system

1> Open the cmd
2> go inside the folder
3> npm i packagename/ npm install packagename


